Date: Sun, 15 Mar 2026 18:39:27 +1300
Subject: [PATCH] feat(api): add Kokoro-style normalization and
 OpenAI-compatible endpoints

- Add Kokoro-inspired text normalization (URLs, emails, numbers, units, phone)
- Add /v1/models, /v1/models/{id}, /v1/audio/speech, /v1/audio/voices
- Improve VQGAN cache keys, reduce per-request overhead, gate debug logs
- Add unit tests and docs update

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
